Class ProvisionalLoadingEvent

  • java.lang.Object

      • com.teamdev.jxbrowser.chromium.events.LoadEvent

  • public final class ProvisionalLoadingEvent
extends LoadEvent
    An event that indicates that provisional load for a specified frame was successfully committed.
    一个事件，指示已成功落实指定帧的临时负载。

      • isSameDocument

        public boolean isSameDocument()
        Indicates whether the loading event is initiated by a navigation within the same document. Navigations within the same document do not change the DOM tree state. The following cases are considered the same document navigation:
        • Reference fragment navigations (e.g. http://www.example.org/foo.html#bar).
        • HTML5 History API: pushState() / replaceState() methods.
        • History navigation within the same page.
        指示加载事件是否由同一文档中的导航启动。同一文档中的导航不会更改DOM树状态。以下情况被视为同一文档导航：参考片段导航（例如http://www.example.org/foo.html#bar）。 HTML5历史记录API：pushState（）/ replaceState（）方法。同一页面内的历史记录导航。
        Returns:
        true if the navigation occurs within the same document. 如果导航发生在同一文档中。
